---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="Nithan Privacy Policy" lang="en">
  <main class="container" style="max-width:760px; padding-top:3rem; padding-bottom:5rem;">
    <h1 style="font-family:'Mali',cursive; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:2rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="policy-content">
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>Nithan values the privacy of all our users. We collect only the minimum information necessary to provide our service, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Website usage data such as pages visited and time spent</li>
        <li>Personal settings stored on your device such as theme and font size (localStorage)</li>
        <li>Information you send us directly, such as email when contacting us</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>2. Use of Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information collected for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>To improve and develop the website</li>
        <li>To analyze usage patterns and enhance performance</li>
        <li>To respond to user inquiries and requests</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
      <p>Our website uses localStorage to store user preferences such as theme and font size. This information is not sent to any server.</p>
      <h2>4. Third-Party Disclosure</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or disclose your personal information to outside parties except when required by law or with your consent.</p>
      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We use appropriate security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, modification, or destruction.</p>
      <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please visit our <a href="/en/contact">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
<style>
  .policy-content h2 { font-family:'Mali',cursive; font-size:1.1rem; color:var(--gold); margin:2rem 0 0.6rem; }
  .policy-content p { margin-bottom:0.8rem; line-height:1.9; }
  .policy-content ul { margin:0.4rem 0 0.8rem 1.5rem; line-height:2; }
</style>
